@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ifhnrs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp(v0) * wp.abs((tmp + 0.94 - v1 + 0.85)))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = 0.35
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.97 + v1 + 0.39)) * v0)
    v2 = v1
    v2 = 0.47
    v0 = (wp.cos(v0) + ((v2 + 0.21 * tmp + 0.24) / (v0 + 0.41 - v0 + 0.94)))
    v0 = (v0 * wp.exp((tmp + 0.69 * v2 + 0.89)))
    data[tid] = v0
